Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你们知道吗
