Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}射那种东西什么用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}叫那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}根本毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我的巨人都倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要我小心一个士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}是的 利威尔兵长很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这家伙就是利威尔吗
