Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}眼睛被砍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我的腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你刚才玩得挺开心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}硬质化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不行 来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那就让我再开心点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}巨人化刚解除时 身体受损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}恢复身体要消耗大量能量 无法巨人化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}喂 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没礼貌的家伙
