Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}一定要杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我发过誓的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么 我还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}有谁还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}居然真的复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他要怎么才会死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们要拿他怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}喂 阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只能赌上一切 让艾伦逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}变瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}超大型巨人变瘦了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}汉吉分队长说得没错
