Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只要能骗过贝鲁特尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就是我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要相信阿尔敏和艾伦会打败贝鲁特尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们只要让莱纳远离阿尔敏他们就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}控制好距离 在他周围飞行 吸引他的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}无视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}直接奔着艾伦去了
