Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}既然没法吸引莱纳的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那就只能在这里把他干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要在这里保护艾伦和阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好 我知道了
