Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}那之后的记忆都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我来把这附近都吹飞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可以的话 让你的巨人的身体仰面躺下扛住爆风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}贝鲁特尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不知道现在是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}也没剩多少力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只要夺走艾伦 就是我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}没错吧 贝鲁特尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我会尽快收拾掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}然后去支援你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}四个人往那边去了 他们是莱纳的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}真没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}从爆风中生还的 只有和艾伦在一起的104期训练兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}说实话 我真想把你们全都吹飞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过 我也习惯这种考验了 阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦已经遍体鳞伤了 把他叫起来能有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你们在死之前会做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这是我自己想出来的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我能撑多久 决定着我们能否成功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}阿尔敏 你难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}抱歉 我在看到海之前是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}所以我会在情况变危险之前逃开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你 你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我并不怎么勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我所认识的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦 你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们不是说好要一起去看海的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我对你撒过谎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}所以 不论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你都要按我的计划行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}果然 胜负已定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他应该是被打成了重度脑震荡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}根本都还站不稳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你很努力地战斗到了最后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦 阿尔敏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 要相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我们的任务是杀死莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要用三支雷枪解决掉莱纳的话 就只有这个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要趁他动不了的时候一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不论结果如何 这都是最后的进攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:15:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}首先我来当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}康尼和萨莎使用两支雷枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}攻击莱纳的下巴两侧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}萨莎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}让
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}有一支没打中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}下巴被炸毁之后 莱纳的嘴巴会张开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}三笠使用最后一支雷枪 从他口中攻击后颈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}嘴巴没有张开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就算这样 也只能一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}阿尔敏没有被吹飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为什么固定器没有脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他明明应该没法靠近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}骨骼不会被消耗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}只要不固定在肌肉上 固定器就不会脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}而且 最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他在释放热风的时候 肌肉无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不过阿尔敏 这就是你的最后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}你绞尽脑汁 最后想出来的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}就是像这样 被灼烧而死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}呼吸好困难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这种程度还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}还要再争取一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}他到底想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}佯攻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦还躺在那里的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}三笠他们也在那边和莱纳苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}真的什么都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}真的就这么结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我这就让你解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}还不能放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}要全部托付给艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我的梦想 生命 一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这就是我能舍弃的一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}艾伦一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}到达海边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}代替我看到海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}三笠 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}不 你们干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}汉吉分队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}趁现在 三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}莱纳 给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}好了 接下来把艾伦和马匹…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}硬质化？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}一开始让我以为艾伦无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}以及阿尔敏的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}都是在争取时间 为了用硬质化制造假的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}一切都是为了让我以为周围已经没有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}为了让我露出破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}我对你撒过谎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord3\shad3\1c&HC0C0C0&\b1}可恶 我本该知道的
